data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome to the highly sought out community of Berry Bay! Spanning 3,800 heated sq.ft., this MI Homes Mira Lago-C floor plan (5 bedrooms, 5 bathrooms) is an exceptional design fit for a variety of lifestyles and families in a true Floridian style! Decorative stone exterior, brick paver driveway and walkway. 6' vinyl PVC fencing around entire backyard. Upon entry you are greeted with immense luxurious design upgrades throughout the entirety of the home.The expansive and spacious two-story floor plan offers easy living with the dining room leading into the luxurious grand room filled with abundant natural light and sliding door access to a covered extended lanai. Upon entering the home, you are greeted by a spacious foyer that leads to a flexible space that can be transformed into formal dining room or playroom with transome windows. The gourmet kitchen featuring a butler’s pantry is equally impressive, with its granite countertops, large island and 42" white cabinets with crown moulding, high-end appliances perfect for preparing meals or entertaining guests, wired for pendant lighting, range hood, built in wall microwave, cook top. The nearby cafe area, with its sliding glass doors that lead out to the 08'X 26" screened lanai, provides a serene space to enjoy your morning coffee. The family room, located adjacent to the kitchen, is the perfect gathering place for family and friends. And for guests, the downstairs second master bedroom has a full bathroom (dual vanities with granite countertops and white cabinets, garden tub, walk in shower with tile listellos, walk in closet. Upstairs, the bedrooms are located, including the spacious owner's suite with tray ceiling, double entry doors, 08'X15" balcony of of master bedroom with views of pond and luxurious bathroom, complete with frameless walk-in shower with matte black hardware and rain shower head, listello tiles, dual granite vanities with white cabinets, and a huge walk-in closet with built in cabinets/organizers. The remaining three bedrooms are separated throughout, with two featuring walk-in closets (one with closet organizer) and the third offering additional space. The three secondary bathrooms have granite countertops, tub/shower combo, white cabinets. Ceramic tile flooring in kitchen and bathrooms. For entertainment and relaxation, the game room with tray ceiling is the perfect space to unwind after a long day. Wrought iron cable stair railing (first and second floor). The home also features a full laundry room with washer and dryer included on first floor. Laminate flooring in living areas and staircase. Lanai plumbed for outdoor sink. Taexx Pest Control System. Berry Bay features superb amenities including - Community Pool , Club house and Bath house - Pickleball and basketball courts - Play ground - Shelters - Mailbox Kiosks - Dog walk stations Don't miss the opportunity to schedule a tour and experience its beauty firsthand.
